{"tid":2127713,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"獨媒係咪有啲鬼鬼地？巫堃泰完全無話過61萬人微不足道..","createTime":"2020-07-27T12:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T14:14:09.000Z","uid":272971,"like":9,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5595c33d701cf1e61ecef0c9ea97f6188f68d14b","tid":2127713,"uid":272971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:50:56.000Z","msg":"民主派早前舉行立法會初選，新界西將派出六張名單。巫堃泰 Michael Mo沒有參加，他解釋，<span class=\"red\">相比去年區議會選舉近190萬名民主派支持者投票，只有61萬人參與初選是微不足道。</span>巫堃泰又稱，深信在120萬名未有投票的民主派支持者當中，一樣有人質疑初選的認受性，故「想畀多個選擇市民」。<br />\n<br />\n【張可森、黃子悅報名參選新西 拒簽確認書】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/303uac3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F303uac3&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=8c0cb12e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/303uac3</a><br />\n<br />\n撐住 #獨媒報導<br />\n定額贊助： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/inmedonate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Finmedonate&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=c6ca1756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/inmedonate</a><br />\n轉數快：9008327<br />\nPaypal 單次贊助： <a href=\"http://paypal.me/inmediahknet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaypal.me%2Finmediahknet&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=20be487e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">paypal.me/inmediahknet</a><br />\nTG：<a href=\"http://t.me/inmediahknet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=1262f6f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/inmediahknet</a><br />\nIG：<a href=\"http://instagram.com/inmediahknet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Finmediahknet%2F&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=2c5ee8b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/inmediahknet/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n獨媒link:<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075875\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075875&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=118d01f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1075875&h=d586a8cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1075875</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">屌你老母當下我睇到<br />\n佢咁樣講話61萬人無用 我即刻嬲左<br />\n想上網搵番佢訪問黎cap圖save低<br />\n點知原來佢只係講<br />\n仲有120萬人可能唔相信呢個初選渣喎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n獨媒你做乜阿 係咪暗啞底紅架？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1oxJ5-GfsHE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1oxJ5-GfsHE&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=b48474eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1oxJ5-GfsHE</a> 訪問第5分45秒開始"},{"pid":"62d3c4a2276d02270984ea7f64c7d281273aa73e","tid":2127713,"uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:52:31.000Z","msg":"佢不嬲都係"},{"pid":"2169b73e3c6c9233247344e2d1870c809b843a6f","tid":2127713,"uid":1984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232f0df98ac77abc91538f03a69ec26809b3d17f","tid":2127713,"uid":102984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:56:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0565248a760a795b3ef922ad530da71070ef31a","tid":2127713,"uid":102984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6118cac66cb3dcc089122e369941411451f3a5f","tid":2127713,"uid":31952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:01:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1d3daf414dcaf51df6c5f28b867d95df144f9f7","tid":2127713,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:02:06.000Z","m